{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Flexbox","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Flexbox","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Flexbox 是 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Flexible Box Layout Module</a> 的常用名称，这是一种用于在单个维度（行或列）中显示项目的布局模型。</p>\n<p>在规范中，Flexbox 被描述为用户界面设计的布局模型。Flexbox 的关键特性是 flex 布局中的项目可以增大和缩小。可以将空间（Space）分配到项目本身、项目之间或项目周围。</p>\n<p>Flexbox 还可以对齐主轴或交叉轴上的项目，从而提供对一组项目大小和对齐的高级控制。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"学习更多","title":"学习更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性引用","title":"属性引用","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-content\"><code>align-content</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-items\"><code>align-items</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-self\"><code>align-self</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex\"><code>flex</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-basis\"><code>flex-basis</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-direction\"><code>flex-direction</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-flow\"><code>flex-flow</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-grow\"><code>flex-grow</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-shrink\"><code>flex-shrink</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-wrap\"><code>flex-wrap</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content\"><code>justify-content</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/order\"><code>order</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"延伸阅读","title":"延伸阅读","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><em><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Flexible Box Layout Module Level 1 Specification</a></em><